    └── 20251028000000_add_app_stats.sql

Project Summary:
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- Database: Supabase
- Landing Page: Full featured landing page with hero, stats, services, reviews
- Main Components: Navbar, Sidebar, TuitionCard, TuitionListItem
- Landing Components: LandingNavbar, LandingHero, LandingStats, LandingServices, LandingReviews, LandingFooter
- Pages: Landing (default), Dashboard, AllTuitions, MyTuitions, Profile, TuitionDetails
- Database Tables: tutor, tuition, app_stats (with RLS policies)
- Real-time Stats: Fetches tutor and student counts from database

Routing:
- "/" -> Landing page (first screen)
- "/dashboard" -> Tutor dashboard (with sidebar/navbar)
- "/tuitions" -> All tuitions list
- "/my-tuitions" -> My tuitions
- "/profile" -> Tutor profile
- Logo click -> Always returns to landing page
